What to wear to a Superbowl party


Sunday February 07 2016




Although Im not a huge football fan dont hate me I do love getting together with friends for a Superbowl party If youre heading out tonight to watch the Broncos play the Panthers here are a few comfy outfit ideas for watching the game in style Of course a team sweatshirt or tee can replace any of the tops here if youre a diehard fan
 

 
Top left nbspGo super casual with a soft leggings or sweats a tee sneakers and jean jacket
Top right nbspGo edgy with nbspfaux leather or waxed skinny jeans or leggings paired with a long sweater and flats or heels Booties would work for this outfit as well
Bottom left nbspA simple sweater dress is perfect for any occasion including a Superbowl party Tone things down with tights riding boots and a scarf 
Bottom right nbspCasual chicjeans a simple sweater a long chunky cardigan and ankle boots make for a cozy and comfy party outfit

Happy Superbowlhope the team nbspyoure rooting for wins
